Do you want a jumpsuit hand painted by a teeny tiny trans non-binary bb? Well you’ve cum to the right place!

I’ve decided to make a couple of handmade crop tops/ jumpsuits and donate the proceeds to a LGBTQ Trans Youth/ Trans Rights Charity organization.
